{"tid":604024,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱好奇睇咗旋風管家個結局 之後成日嘅心情就咁冇哂","createTime":"2018-03-24T10:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T18:47:12.000Z","uid":102208,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"a404c23fa7d777b27a9ad8e2544eb6d8394c5640","tid":604024,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T10:08:02.000Z","msg":"我細個嘅時候就係比依套野搞到對動漫好有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每集睇住佢咁多角色係到搞下笑 整蠱做怪<br />\n和和氣氣 團團結結嘅時候<br />\n無論幾唔開心都會笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知今日睇漫畫嘅時候<br />\n無意中比我發現返依套野<br />\n之後就抱著好奇心直接入去睇結局<br />\n<br />\n我好驚訝<br />\n先唔講會長嘅表白比作者輕輕帶過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解一套搞笑日常動漫嘅結局會係咁嘅收尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞個比喻 就好似一個美好家庭突然支離破碎咁<br />\n各有各生活<br />\n雖然我都認為啊颯同三千院一齊<br />\n算係一個good end<br />\n但唔知點解都會有心[up]嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望作者會繼續出埋其他角色嘅日後談啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kZBwnLzDGOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkZBwnLzDGOk&d=4P%2FVYxtlXed%2B3naUXCYKwZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=853a86e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kZBwnLzDGOk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有啲咩講錯記得屌細力啲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">利申會長派<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"dfd2336221885c1bf9d0bd6078a2120a75dd69f4","tid":604024,"uid":34293,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"瑪莉亞派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab91360a36cb048e73ef533c98c87e3e78445a0","tid":604024,"uid":33651,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2